dalserver.tap

Class TapTableWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • dalserver.tap.TapTableWriter

  • public class TapTableWriter
extends java.lang.Object
    DALServer implementation of the OpenCADC/TAP TableWriter interface. This implementation uses the DALServer parameter mechanism for configuration parameters, and the DALServer RequestResponse, serializer, and table configuration mechanisms for table output.

      • setJob

        public void setJob(Job job)
        Set a reference to the UWS Job context.
        Parameters:
        job - Job instance The Job context is the primary mechanism for communicating context information to TAP class code. In particular, a reference to the DalContext for the query and service instance is stored in the Job descriptor, making it possible for DALServer TAP plugins to retrieve the DALServer context.
